{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/pullrequests/75/comments/4726572.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gzweb/diff/osrf/gzweb:853b6668e4aa..6e4ec610eca1?path=gz3d%2Fbuild%2Fgz3d.js"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb/pull-requests/75/_/diff#comment-4726572"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 75, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/pullrequests/75.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb/pull-requests/75"}}, "title": "Fix loading heightmap with one texture"}, "content": {"raw": "humm I think we can use the target as we are currently doing, at least with our revision of three.js. According to [this discussion](https://github.com/mrdoob/three.js/pull/1437#issuecomment-4303052), directional lights have targets just like spotlights.\n\nTake the following light as an example:\n\n~~~\n    <light type=\"directional\" name=\"directional\">\n      <pose>10 10 10 0 0 0</pose>\n      <direction>0 0 -1</direction>\n      (...)\n    </light>\n~~~\n\non default it appears properly directed to -z:\n\n![directionalLight1.png](data/bitbucket.org/repo/r77Gja/images/1824079702-directionalLight1.png)\n\nbut on this branch it points from (10, 10, 10) towards (0, 0, 0):\n\n![directionalLight2.png](data/bitbucket.org/repo/r77Gja/images/4040191966-directionalLight2.png)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>humm I think we can use the target as we are currently doing, at least with our revision of three.js. According to <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://github.com/mrdoob/three.js/pull/1437#issuecomment-4303052\" rel=\"nofollow\">this discussion</a>, directional lights have targets just like spotlights.</p>\n<p>Take the following light as an example:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;light</span> <span class=\"na\">type=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;directional&quot;</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;directional&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;pose&gt;</span>10 10 10 0 0 0<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/pose&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;direction&gt;</span>0 0 -1<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/direction&gt;</span>\n      (...)\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/light&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>on default it appears properly directed to -z:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"directionalLight1.png\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/r77Gja/images/1824079702-directionalLight1.png\" /></p>\n<p>but on this branch it points from (10, 10, 10) towards (0, 0, 0):</p>\n<p><img alt=\"directionalLight2.png\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/r77Gja/images/4040191966-directionalLight2.png\" /></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-01-20T23:49:54.474835+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": 6086, "path": "gz3d/build/gz3d.js"}, "updated_on": "2015-01-20T23:49:54.486141+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 4726572}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/pullrequests/75/comments/4727162.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gzweb/diff/osrf/gzweb:None..None?path=gz3d%2Fbuild%2Fgz3d.js"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb/pull-requests/75/_/diff#comment-4727162"}}, "parent": {"id": 4726572, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/pullrequests/75/comments/4726572.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb/pull-requests/75/_/diff#comment-4726572"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 75, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/pullrequests/75.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb/pull-requests/75"}}, "title": "Fix loading heightmap with one texture"}, "content": {"raw": "ok I see, I was probably looking at outdated api doc. Currently the terrain shader makes use of the directional light's position for shading, I'll change that too", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>ok I see, I was probably looking at outdated api doc. Currently the terrain shader makes use of the directional light's position for shading, I'll change that too</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-01-21T00:43:34.770741+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Ian Chen", "uuid": "{eaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Beaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Beaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:10b01d41-a2e9-4a41-a907-e6e2f03b6cd5/1e4adcdf-1946-4280-9aea-eb5f15a7f912/128"}}, "nickname": "Ian Chen", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:10b01d41-a2e9-4a41-a907-e6e2f03b6cd5"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "gz3d/build/gz3d.js"}, "updated_on": "2015-01-21T00:43:34.777403+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 4727162}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/pullrequests/75/comments/4727207.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gzweb/diff/osrf/gzweb:None..None?path=gz3d%2Fbuild%2Fgz3d.js"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb/pull-requests/75/_/diff#comment-4727207"}}, "parent": {"id": 4727162, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gzweb/pullrequests/75/comments/4727162.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gzweb/pull-requests/75/_/diff#commen